Sub 'GetCliente'
For each order EmpCod,PesCod where EmpCod = &EmpCod where PesCod = &AgeCliCod if PesCodRaz.Length() > 40 &PesCodRaz = substr(PesCodRaz,1,37) + '(...) : ' else &PesCodRaz = Trim(PesCodRaz) + ': ' EndIF exit EndFor
EndSub
